{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "法尔吉德 第4话 为了不再后悔",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "喂～再多拿点过来！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "来啦！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "嘿嘿，我要开动啦。\\n啊呜啊呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "呵呵，看到来客是龙我还挺吃惊的，\\n不过见你吃得这么畅快，\\n我看着也很高兴呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "今天我要庆祝一番。\\n总算甩掉麻烦获得了自由，\\n要好好享受这来之不易的自由啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "这样啊。虽然不知道你说的是什么，\\n不过你也挺不容易的吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "何止是不容易啊。再那样下去\\n我随时都有可能丢掉小命，\\n法尔吉德那小子真是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "诶？法尔吉德难道是……\\n那个总是笑眯眯、\\n性格又很好的男孩子？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "你认识法尔吉德吗？\\n我说的是某个为了救人\\n会冲出去挡大炮的家伙……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "啊……那果然就是\\n我认识的那个人呢。\\n他过得还好吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "好倒是好，\\n但他要是一直当烂好人，\\n总有一天会吃苦头的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "是吗……难道他还在\\n介意那时候的事……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "嗯？你和法尔吉德\\n是什么关系啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "我们是同一家孤儿院的。\\n从记事起就在一起生活，\\n可以说就像家人一样。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "喔……从小就和那种家伙\\n待在一起一定很辛苦吧？\\n是不是总被他折腾？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "倒也没有。他以前很内向，\\n不和任何人讲话。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "啊！？你说那家伙！？\\n真的假的？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "真的，要说的话就是胆小，\\n不管做什么都要看周围人的脸色，\\n总是最后才做出决定。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "不会吧……\\n那不是和现在正相反嘛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "他发生转变，\\n应该是那次事故后……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "事故？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "嗯，记得是他七八岁那年……\\n孤儿院的几个孩子在山里\\n玩的时候发生了大规模泥石流。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "大家都认为那些孩子们\\n一定是死于泥石流了。\\n但是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "其实当时他们碰巧在山洞里，\\n没有被卷入泥石流。\\n可是泥沙堵住了洞口。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "不仅逃不出去，那些大人们\\n也以为他们已经死了，\\n连搜救都没进行。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "但是，那之后\\n过了十天左右……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "有个地方发生了小型泥石流，\\n去查看情况的人\\n听到了孩子的声音。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "得救了吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "对，不过只有法尔吉德一个人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "好像就是从那之后吧，\\n他像变了一个人似的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "他是想……\\n替死去的那些人活下去？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "应该也有这个原因……\\n不过他说当时他放弃了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "好像是觉得已经没救了，\\n不管做什么都没用，\\n就没有采取任何行动。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "可其他孩子们不是这样。\\n他们大声地呼救，\\n还试图挖通被堵住的洞口。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "但是泥石流本身就导致\\n土质疏松了，再大声呼救\\n还胡乱挖掘的话……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "连挖掘的部分\\n也塌了吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "没错，结果努力不放弃的\\n孩子们死了，只剩什么都\\n没做的法尔吉德活了下来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "他觉得没有资格获救的自己\\n反倒活了下来，真正应该获救的\\n是那些没有放弃的孩子们。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "原来如此……\\n所以他才会做那种……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "我已经不想\\n再眼睁睁地看着\\n却无所作为了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110393_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔吉德",
            "context": "我不想再因为我什么都没做，\\n而只剩自己独活……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "啧……那家伙搞什么。\\n结果不还是和从前一样，\\n是个笨蛋嘛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "他是想说他应该和其他人\\n一起坚持挖洞，然后一起\\n被埋才好吗？才不是这样吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "是啊……\\n谁都不希望他死掉。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "到头来，他根本不相信任何人，\\n固执地认为所有人\\n都会比他早死。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "大家才没有他想得\\n那么脆弱……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "是啊……\\n那个……龙先生，请你告诉\\n法尔吉德这一点吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "让、让我告诉他！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "嗯，我觉得\\n他一定是信任你的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "虽然我不太了解，\\n不过你因为他的缘故\\n遇到危险了吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "他应该是心里隐约觉得\\n只要是你就没问题，\\n才会那么做的吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "啧……\\n真是个不让人省心的小子。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "呵呵，是啊，\\n不过，正因为这样\\n才没法不管他吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "放着不管他绝对会死，\\n而且他也没烦到让人想丢下他。\\n真是的，摊上这么个大麻烦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "女服务生",
            "context": "就请你多关照他一点了，龙先生。\\n看他似乎交了一位\\n不错的朋友，我也很开心。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "朋友吗……\\n不太准确。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120223_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴比",
            "context": "我和法尔吉德……\\n是一心同体的搭档！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}